{"legislative_session": "2026", "identifier": "SB2071", "title": "RELATING TO HOUSING.", "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}", "classification": ["bill"], "subject": ["Fee Simple", "HHFDC", "Housing", "Leasehold", "Option Period", "Rent-to-Own Program"], "abstracts": [{"note": "description", "abstract": "Clarifies that the dwelling units eligible for the Rent-to-Own Program shall be units that are for sale in fee simple or leasehold on non-ceded state or county land under a lease with an initial term of not less than 99 years.  Replaces the five-year period during which the sales price of a rent-to-own dwelling unit shall remain fixed with an option period established by the Hawaii Housing Finance and Development Corporation.  Effective 7/1/2050.  (SD1)"}], "other_titles": [], "other_identifiers": [{"identifier": "ocd-bill-hi-2026-sb2071"}], "actions": [{"description": "Report adopted; Passed Second Reading, as amended (SD 1) and referred to WAM.", "date": "2026-02-17", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}", "classification": ["passage", "reading-2", "referral-committee"], "related_entities": [{"name": "Ways and Means", "entity_type": "organization", "organization_id": null}]}, {"description": "Reported from HOU/CPN (Stand. Com. Rep. No. 2282) with recommendation of passage on Second Reading, as amended (SD 1) and referral to WAM.", "date": "2026-02-17", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "The committee(s) on  CPN recommend(s) that the measure be PASSED, WITH AMENDMENTS.  The votes in CPN were as follows: 5 Aye(s): Senator(s) Keohokalole, Fukunaga, Lamosao, McKelvey, Awa; Aye(s) with reservations: none ; 0 No(es): none; and 0 Excused: none.", "date": "2026-02-03", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}", "classification": ["committee-passage-favorable"], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "The committee(s) on  HOU recommend(s) tha